history.content:
It's definitely doable if you don't have other techs.

__

I took those together and it was definitely manageable. 127 homework is once every two weeks so it's easy to balance out the work. Also 127, when I took it, had a midterm and 2 quizzes whereas 170 had 2 midterms so the exams didn't happen in the same week.

It's definitely doable if you don't have other techs.
